  "texts": [
    "Gao et al. (2022) utilized the global mask to obtain more comprehensive clothing features rather than being limited to the center point.",
    "Match-RCNN (Godi et al. 2022) connects store images with video sequences to remove the reliance on annotated bounding boxes in previous fashion retrieval datasets.",
    "The difference between cross-scenario and intra-scenario fashion retrieval lies in the scenario of the query and candidate images.",
    "In practice, it is challenging to handle the discrepancies between fashion items in different scenarios.",
    "One commonly used strategy is the use of domain adaptation techniques, in which triple embeddings are adopted to bridge the discrepancies between domains."
